              Diam nunc lacus lacus aliquam turpis enim. Eget hac velit est euismod lacus. Est non placerat nam arcu. Cras
              purus nibh cursus sit eu in id. Integer vel nibh.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mx-auto mt-16 flex max-w-2xl flex-col gap-8 lg:mx-0 lg:mt-20 lg:max-w-none lg:flex-row lg:items-end">
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse justify-between gap-x-16 gap-y-8 rounded-2xl bg-brand-50 dark:bg-brand-800 p-8 sm:w-3/4 sm:max-w-md sm:flex-row-reverse sm:items-end lg:w-72 lg:max-w-none lg:flex-none lg:flex-col lg:items-start">
              <p class="flex-none text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-content-primary dark:text-content-inverse">250k</p>
              <div class="sm:w-80 sm:shrink lg:w-auto lg:flex-none">
